(CGMCC 3.20157). a Yellow colony on a fruiting body of 
<taxonomicName box="[1057,1163,1563,1584]" class="Agaricomycetes" family="Boletaceae" genus="Boletus" kingdom="Fungi" order="Boletales" pageId="8" pageNumber="36" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="species" species="undetermined">
